data.description: So many updates to this charming Morningside bungalow.  The front entrance invites you into the living room which opens up to the eat in kitchen. Off the kitchen is access to the 16x12 deck that overlooks the backyard and above ground pool. Just off the pool area there is additional off-street parking and a shed to house all those extra pool toys. The exterior of the home has had many updates including, roof 2017, windows & siding 2021, gutters 2023. The furnace was new in 2023 as well. The main floor has 2 of the 3 bedrooms and a full bath with a whirlpool tub and heated floors. The upstairs is currently the oversized 3rd bedroom that was used as a daycare in past years. In the lower level you will find a large living room with a bar for entertaining and another full bathroom. This property does have an extra-long driveway in which you can house your camper, boat or any additional vehicles. A must see that is bigger than it looks from the outside.
